PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775736665
OL,3,CShipwreck with explosives aboard set
OL,4,Cto have masts reduced in #9.5 million
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,FSalvage efforts were abandoned when
OL,8,Fthe vessel flooded completely just
OL,9,Fover a month later, and around 1,400
OL,10,Ftons of explosives are still thought
OL,11,Fto be contained in the SS Richard
OL,12,FMontgomery's forward holds.
OL,14,FA DfT spokesperson said: "Our priority
OL,15,Fwill always be to ensure the safety of
OL,16,Fthe public and to reduce any risk
OL,17,Fposed by the SS Richard Montgomery.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
