OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775736665
OL,3,CShipwreck with explosives aboard set
OL,4,Cto have masts reduced in #9.5 million
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,F"The condition of the wreck remains
OL,8,Fstable, experts are continuing to
OL,9,Fmonitor the site, and we have now
OL,10,Foutlined our intention to choose the
OL,11,FResolve Group to undertake the mast
OL,12,Fremoval project.
OL,14,F"Further updates will be delivered in
OL,15,Fdue course."
OL,17,FAnnual condition surveys have not
OL,18,Findicated that the risk associated
OL,19,Fwith the wreck has increased,
OL,20,Faccording to the department.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
