PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775736665
OL,3,CShipwreck with explosives aboard set
OL,4,Cto have masts reduced in #9.5 million
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,FA restriction of flying order is in
OL,8,Fplace above the site, with pilots and
OL,9,Fdrone operators diverted from
OL,10,Foverflying the wreck.
OL,12,FThe SS Richard Montgomery lies around
OL,13,F1.5 miles off the coast of Sheerness
OL,14,Fon the Isle of Sheppey, Kent.
OL,16,FKevin McKenna, the Labour MP for
OL,17,FSittingbourne and Sheppey, has called
OL,18,Ffor one of the masts to be kept on the
OL,19,Fisland.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
