OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775736665
OL,3,CShipwreck with explosives aboard set
OL,4,Cto have masts reduced in #9.5 million
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,F"For many people on Sheppey, the
OL,8,FMontgomery masts are far more than
OL,9,Fwreckage, they're a cherished landmark
OL,10,Flinked to an extraordinary wartime
OL,11,Fstory," he told the Press Association.
OL,13,F"I fully support their safe removal
OL,14,Fand believe it's vital that part of
OL,15,Fthis iconic structure is preserved for
OL,16,Ffuture generations.
OL,26,@sD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1775736665
OL,3,CShipwreck with explosives aboard set
OL,4,Cto have masts reduced in #9.5 million
OL,5,Cdeal
OL,7,F"That's why I'm calling on the
OL,8,FGovernment to secure one of the
OL,9,FMontgomery masts for display in a
OL,10,Flocal museum, so that this island's
OL,11,Funique history can be shared and
OL,12,Fremembered by the people of Sheppey
OL,13,Ffor generations to come."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
